sequenceDiagram
    participant M as ADW300
    participant E as Node-RED Edge
    participant I as Ingestion Service
    participant TD as Telemetry DB
    participant J as Worker Jobs

    M->>E: Envoi de trames partielles
    E->>E: Normalisation et fusion
    E->>I: Batch toutes les 10 minutes
    I->>TD: Insertion des mesures
    I->>J: Signal de traitement asynchrone
    J->>TD: Aggregations et enrichissements
